HEADWORD: Solidary
<hw>Sol"i*da*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having community
of interests and responsibilities.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q> Men are <qex>solidary</qex>, or copartners; and not isolated.</q>
